Creation a reusable Measure as Master Item 8


Master Item  Measure  is a reusable measure that once created it can be used on  multiple chart or within multiple  sheets. 


What to  build 




INSPECTION_RATE      Master Item reusable Measure  


INJURY_RATE      Master Item reusable Measure  


All  this measure  should  be created following  the gift  example 

Injury Rate %        Sum(INJURE) /Count( Total INJURE )
Inspection Rate %   Sum(INSPECTION) / Count( Total  INSPECTION)


Creating a master measure from a field
